ProcedureHelp.#cdata:
Syntax: PROC MODECLUS <options> ; 
    BY variables ; 
    FREQ variable ; 
    ID variable ; 
    VAR variables ; 

The MODECLUS procedure clusters observations in a SAS data set by using any of several algorithms 
based on nonparametric density estimates.

StatementHelp.#cdata:
Syntax: VAR variables ;

The VAR statement specifies numeric variables to be used in the cluster analysis. If you omit the 
VAR statement, all numeric variables not specified in other statements are used.
